Description: macOS-style fullscreen application launcher for Linux
 LinxPad is a fullscreen application launcher for Linux supporting both
 X11 and Wayland. It provides a grid of application icons with folder
 grouping, drag-and-drop reordering, multi-page navigation, integrated
 search, and a settings panel.
